ta
experience. I first met with editor Jonathan Wingfield in June 2024, and by=
 the autumn, he and his cofounders didn=E2=80=99t work at System anymore. F=
or several months, I was writing ( https://puck.news/newsletter_content/a-c=
onde-identity-crisis-lvmh-internal-monologues-karlies-new-creatives-2/?1739=
