or the magazine, disclosing information I=E2=80=99m sure no one involved wa=
nted me to
divulge. In the end, Wingfield, Elizabeth von Guttman, and Thomas Lenthal w=
on ( https://puck.news/newsletter_content/biebers-glow-up-sezane-mania-some=
-holiday-recs-2/?utm_campaign=3DLine+Sheet+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%282%2F10%2F25%29&=
