_action&utm_source=3Dcustomer.io&utm_term=3Df6c60617da42abd12a ) the fight,=
 and I did a second interview. They let me do my job, and I let them do the=
irs. I appreciate their interest! [System]

=C2=A0

Pieter Mulier partnered with photographer Anthony Seklaoui to release a boo=
k of imagery documenting his time at Ala=C3=AFa, all the way through the Gu=
ggenheim show. (On Thursday, February 13, in Paris, they=E2=80=99re hosting=
 a book signing at the Saint-Honor=C3=A9 store.) For collectors, Mulier=E2=
=80=99s moment at Ala=C3=AFa is unique in the history of fashion, and I sus=
pect the value of this actual tome will appreciate fast.
